CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773670277
OL,3,CDrug driver who caused death of
OL,4,Cbrother and 12-year-old nephew jailed
OL,6,FA dangerous driver who has been
OL,7,Fdescribed as an "accident waiting to
OL,8,Fhappen" has been jailed over a crash
OL,9,Fthat killed his brother and nephew.
OL,11,FMichael Webb was four times over the
OL,12,Fdrug drive limit when he lost control
OL,13,Fof his Skoda Octavia while attempting
OL,14,Fto undertake a BMW on 30 August 2025.
OL,16,FNewcastle Crown Court heard the 35-
OL,17,Fyear-old was likely to have been
OL,18,Fdriving at about 73mph on the 40mph-
OL,19,Flimit John Reid Road in South Shields.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773670277
OL,3,CDrug driver who caused death of
OL,4,Cbrother and 12-year-old nephew jailed
OL,6,FThe car tore in two when it crashed
OL,7,Finto a tree, killing Webb's brother,
OL,8,FPeter Webb, 40, and Peter's 12-year-
OL,9,Fold son, Ben.
OL,11,FWebb, of Park Avenue, South Shields,
OL,12,Fwas jailed for 13 years and six months
OL,13,Fafter pleading guilty to two counts of
OL,14,Fcausing death by dangerous driving on
OL,15,F12 March.
OL,17,FAshleigh Webb, Peter's wife and Ben's
OL,18,Fmother, tearfully told the court that
OL,19,F"no sentence will ever be long enough"
OL,20,Fas she said Webb's driving had always
OL,21,Fbeen "an accident waiting to happen".
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@fO]}D@FOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773670277
OL,3,CDrug driver who caused death of
OL,4,Cbrother and 12-year-old nephew jailed
OL,6,FShe described her horror when police
OL,7,Fofficers arrived at her home to say
OL,8,Fher husband had been in a crash, and
OL,9,Frealising their son was with him.
OL,11,F"He drove so dangerously and with so
OL,12,Flittle consideration for anyone. He
OL,13,Ftook my little boy away," Mrs Webb
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"Ben had no choice about getting in
OL,17,Fthat car. You were the adult and it
OL,18,Fwas your responsibility to protect him.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773670277
OL,3,CDrug driver who caused death of
OL,4,Cbrother and 12-year-old nephew jailed
OL,6,F"I will never get the answers I search
OL,7,Ffor. Was my little boy scared? Did he
OL,8,Fshout for me? Was Peter shouting to
OL,9,Fslow down?"
OL,11,FShe told the court she had not
OL,12,Freceived an apology from Webb, and
OL,13,Fthat images had been posted online of
OL,14,Fhim smoking cannabis and drinking
OL,15,Fwhile on bail, saying it "shows a
OL,16,Fcomplete lack of remorse".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773670277
OL,3,CDrug driver who caused death of
OL,4,Cbrother and 12-year-old nephew jailed
OL,6,FMrs Webb told her brother-in-law:
OL,7,F"Peter previously made it known he
OL,8,Fdidn't like the way you drove...
OL,9,FMichael, you have always been this way
OL,10,Fwith cars.
OL,12,F"You were an accident waiting to
OL,13,Fhappen."
OL,15,FShe said she had been "genuinely
OL,16,Fterrified" as a passenger in his car
OL,17,Fbefore and asked him to slow down, but
OL,18,Fhe would just "laugh and continue".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUuD@HO]wD@WOUxD@JO]zD@OOUzD@
OL,26,AbO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773670277
OL,3,CDrug driver who caused death of
OL,4,Cbrother and 12-year-old nephew jailed
OL,6,F"I felt you enjoyed the power you had
OL,7,Fof your passengers being helpless,"
OL,8,Fshe said.
OL,10,FMrs Webb added: "No sentence will ever
OL,11,Fbe long enough in my eyes for the
OL,12,Fdestruction and recklessness he has
OL,13,Fcaused."
OL,15,FDuring the fatal incident, Webb lost
OL,16,Fcontrol of the car and hit a lamppost,
OL,17,Fthen a tree, with the impact tearing
OL,18,Fthe car in two and killing his
OL,19,Fbrother: joiner Peter Webb, who was in
OL,20,Fthe front passenger seat wearing a
OL,21,Fseatbelt.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@cO]rD@QOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773670277
OL,3,CDrug driver who caused death of
OL,4,Cbrother and 12-year-old nephew jailed
OL,6,FMs Dowling said Ben Webb, was sitting
OL,7,Fin the back seat and was propelled,
OL,8,Fwith the rear of the car, back into
OL,9,Fthe carriageway.
OL,11,FThe court heard Webb had joined his
OL,12,Fbrother and nephew who were watching
OL,13,Ffootball at a pub earlier in the day.
OL,15,FHe drank one pint, before going back
OL,16,Fto his house and returning later to
OL,17,Fpick them up at about 8.50pm.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773670277
OL,3,CDrug driver who caused death of
OL,4,Cbrother and 12-year-old nephew jailed
OL,6,FWebb, who was also injured in the
OL,7,Fcrash, was found to have a "very low"
OL,8,Flevel of alcohol in his blood, but was
OL,9,Ffound to be more than double the limit
OL,10,Ffor cocaine, and four times the limit
OL,11,Ffor cocaine breakdown product,
OL,12,FBenzoylecgonine.
OL,14,FJudge Tim Gittins told Webb: "You
OL,15,Fshould have been nowhere near the
OL,16,Fdriving seat of any vehicle, let alone
OL,17,Fone carrying two passengers."
OL,26,@oD@\OUoD@eO]vD@^OUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773670277
OL,3,CDrug driver who caused death of
OL,4,Cbrother and 12-year-old nephew jailed
OL,6,FThe judge said: "The stark reality is
OL,7,Fthat you were a serious or fatal
OL,8,Faccident waiting to happen that night
OL,9,Fby the manner of your driving.
OL,11,F"It was, sadly, an entirely avoidable
OL,12,Ftragedy."
OL,14,FJudge Gittins banned Webb from driving
OL,15,Ffor 15 years and five months, and said
OL,16,Fhe must take an extended driving test
OL,17,Fbefore he can get behind the wheel
OL,18,Fagain.
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOUtD@IO]
